{
  "stem": "11882.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Kempner was never discouraged about this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He felt-- he called it the-- what did he call it-- the-- the pity, the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everybody was calling for pity for these poor men, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they didn't spend very long-- some of them died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a very harsh thing for them, psychologically, in the world press and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he always felt that Nuremberg's contribution to society was that it showed the documentation of this thing, and it was a warning that crime is crime, even if big government employees manipulate it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he felt that was Nuremberg's prime contribution to law, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Recently, I read the most horrible thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kempner has one or two volumes in my apartment, and I was going through them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had marked-- he prepared me for this-- he had marked-- I should have read it before I came-- he had marked the pages where some of these very frank witnesses, true believers in Nazism and anti-Semitism and the Holocaust-- in the real sense, believers that it should be done, that it was a great deed, the Holocaust-- told how when they ran out-- This man told of his-- I don't even remember his name, I'm sorry to say.",
      "word_count": 80
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could supply you with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's in this volume.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There are many volumes of the records of the Nuremberg Trials, you know, of subsequent proceedings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there it showed how when they ran out of their Zyklon-B gas, or whatever it was, they had to kill so-and-so many people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were so-and-so many there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were coming in every day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were under duress.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were dutiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they smashed the babies against the wall to kill them quick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, that was to me the most horrible thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
